{"tid":2133191,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國駐英大使劉曉明：中國未來不會視BNO為合法旅行證件。中國是英國的未來。","createTime":"2020-07-31T02:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T01:14:52.000Z","uid":48040,"like":58,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3fcc01f57f1719b3994b8ada73420b1e8d2298","tid":2133191,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:12:41.000Z","msg":"中國駐英大使劉曉明表示，中英關係近日面臨嚴峻形勢，責任完全在英方，他再次批評英國無端指責「港區國安法」，妄稱中方違反《中英聯合聲明》是完全錯誤，又指英方改變BNO政策及暫停與香港的引渡協定，是粗暴干涉香港事務及中國內政；而英國在涉疆問題上罔顧事實、顛倒黑白，嚴重毒化中英關係氛圍。<span class=\"orange\">他強調，中國未來不會將BNO護照視為合法的旅行證件。</span><br />\n<br />\n英國如果拒斥中國，就是拒斥未來。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2349814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2349814&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=e2c7de9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2349814</a>"},{"pid":"6a33fb8ea11dd1e26913a1229efa03bb19cfbe30","tid":2133191,"uid":19126,"like":191,"dislike":2,"score":189,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"即係未來係計劃吞埋英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b93f4ba86758e464742519ad75c9d46d0d01f88","tid":2133191,"uid":70745,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:13:34.000Z","msg":"真荒謬，把自己看得這麼高.jif"},{"pid":"9794b72e77fd463b2e30d7bc14436f3564b0699e","tid":2133191,"uid":48040,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"6a33fb8ea11dd1e26913a1229efa03bb19cfbe30","tid":2133191,"uid":19126,"like":191,"dislike":2,"score":189,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"即係未來係計劃吞埋英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:13:50.000Z","msg":"自古以來英國係中國的"},{"pid":"58ccb2614647197cc2d99b237a07a3c8a4c9135c","tid":2133191,"uid":48040,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:14:22.000Z","msg":"twitter戰線<br />\n<a href=\"